   During the past decade, pioneering businesses have succeeded at making
   money while conserving and sustainably using biodiversity. What lessons
   have we learned! How can we speed up the adoption of
   biodiversity-friendly business activities' Where and how can additional
   private investment for biodiversity conservation and sustainable use be
